 3^2=a^2+c^2\\4^2=b^2+c^2\\5^2=b^2+d^2\\x^2=a^2+d^2 
 c^2 = 3^2 - a^2\quad\land\quad c^2 = 4^2 - b^2\\then\\ [I]\quad3^2 - a^2 = 4^2 - b^2\\AND\\ d^2 = 5^2 - b^2\quad\land\quad d^2 = x^2 - a^2\\then\\ [II]\quad5^2 - b^2 = x^2 - a^2 
 5^2 - x^2 = b^2 - a^2\quad\Rightarrow\quad 5^2 - x^2 = 4^2 - 3^2\\x=3\sqrt2 
